episodes.title: How my Mom got into a Medical Cult
episodes.description:
Guys my mom fell into the world of homeopathy, and it completely changed the way I think. 

In this video, I break down how she got involved, why homeopathy doesn’t actually work, and the dangers of believing in medical cults. We’ll also talk about the placebo effect, how misinformation spreads, and how you can implement your own pseudociences to your advantage. 

If you’ve ever wondered how smart people fall for pseudoscience, this video is for you.
